---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Directory Data Enrichment Service" description="Optional directory data enrichment service for structured listing data, field normalization, and quality assurance.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-14"><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><span class="text-sm text-[#00f0ff] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-wider">DATA SERVICE</span><h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mt-4 mb-5 font-['Space_Grotesk']">Directory Data Enrichment Service</h1><p class="text-[#8b8b9a] text-lg max-w-3xl">Data enrichment is optional and scoped transparently. If you already have data, I import and map it. If not, I can enrich listings with clear per-item pricing.</p></div></section>
  <section class="py-10"><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6"><h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">Basic enrichment</h2><p class="text-[#8b8b9a] mb-2">$0.50 / listing</p><ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]"><li>• Name, address, website, phone</li><li>• Category normalization</li><li>• Clean import formatting</li></ul></div><div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6"><h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">Premium enrichment</h2><p class="text-[#8b8b9a] mb-2">$1.00 / listing</p><ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]"><li>• Everything in basic</li><li>• Attributes and descriptions</li><li>• QA pass before import</li></ul></div></div></section>
  <section class="py-14"><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3"><a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0a0a0f] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00f0ff] to-[#00c8ff] rounded-xl">See all add-ons</a><a href="mailto:tim@stackbasesystem.com" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl">Request data scope</a></div></section>
</Layout>
